## ğŸ¯ Daily Workflow Commands

### Morning Routine (Pull)
```bash
# 1. Pull global config
cd ~/projects
git pull

# 2. Pull all project code
sync-all pull

# 3. Read yesterday's session
cat ~/projects/ovu/docs/SESSION_HANDOFF.md

# 4. Open Cursor
cursor ~/projects/ovu/ovu-workspace.code-workspace
```

### Evening Routine (Push)
```bash
# 1. Save session
session-save ~/projects/ovu

# 2. Push all project code
sync-all push "Description of what was done"

# 3. Push global config (if changed)
cd ~/projects
git add .
git commit -m "Update global config"
git push
```

